        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Petition for appointment of J. Hunter as surveyor.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>To his <persName>Honor Col. Stephen F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>We the <persName>people of <placeName>San Jacinto</placeName></persName> and Vicinity humbly beg leave to
represent that Whereas in our humble opinion the lands in this 
Section of your Honor's <placeName>Colony</placeName>&#8212;are of a quality not to warrant a
general Survey of the whole and whereas as we humbly suppose
there will be <persName>emegrants </persName>dropping in from time to time requiring
more or less locations in this Section of the Country and in that case
a local <persName>surveyor </persName>will be very convenient both to ourselves and to those
who may hereafter come. Therefore if it is not contrary to the 
regulations of your Honor we humbly beg the apointment of such an
one amongst our Citizens&#8212;we nominate to your Honor <persName>Doct. J.
Hunter</persName> who is one of the first <persName>settlers </persName>here,</p>

<p>and so as in duty Bound we will forever Pray Oct. the <date n="xx-xx-1824">anno
Domini 1824</date></p>

<p><persName>D. E. Bayles </persName>                                <persName>John Williams</persName>
<persName>Page Ballew </persName>                                <persName>John E. Harris</persName>
